    <ul>
      <li>- B.Sc. in Physics, Universidad Pedagógica y Tecnológica de Colombia, Tunja, Colombia </li>
      <li>- Diploma in Earth System Physics, International Centre for Theoretical Physics, Trieste, Italy</li>
      <li>- Ph.D in Earth Science and Fluid Mechanics, Università degli Studi di Trieste, Trieste, Italy </li>
      <li>- Postdoctoral Researcher, Istituto Nazionale di Oceanografia e Geofisica Sperimentale, Trieste, Italy</li>
    </ul> -->

  <p class='text-lg mt-6' style='text-align: justify;'>
    Feel free to explore my work and connect with me through the links below. 
  </p>
 
  <div class='flex gap-4'>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
  <p class='text-lg mt-6' style='text-align: justify;'> 
    Take a peek at my personal blog to see what else I'm into other than work 👨‍👩‍👦‍👦🧗🏾‍♀️🏔️⛷️🚵🏾‍♀️.
  </p>
</div>


<div class='size-72 lg:block hidden'>
  <!-- Add your profile image -->
  <Image
    src={profilePicture}
    alt={fullName}
    class='w-full h-full mask mask-circle size-44'
  />
</div>